{
  "stem": "12768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we called them and asked if they could-- if they would give their name to the police, and if we could use their name, then we would get train tickets to come to Gothenburg.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we told them that we will call again and let them know when the train was leaving, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they picked us up, and we walked then, afterwards, to their house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we got there, there was already at-- the apartment was full, it was like we were Norwegian sardines in a can.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was how many people there were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were eating in shifts, because we couldn't all eat at the same time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was not room for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So right away, we all tried to see if we could find, and then my brother and my friend left us and went to his family, which has also come over to Sweden.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it's just my brother Paul and I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got one room in an apartment that was rented for us, and my father got another room in another place that was rented for him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so then we-- we got some money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, of course, we started right away looking for work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my brother got a job, and I got a job, and my father got a job.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even though not so many-- my father was more or less like a helper, but it all helped, you know, to sustain ourselves, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And even though-- and we got help from the Swedish government, I must say.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were very nice to us, you know, and helped us with a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we could buy clothes at a very reasonable price that they set for-- for us new immigrants into Sweden.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
